<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-TW">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>社群互動 | 貼文瀏覽</title>

  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/base.css') }}">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="{{ url_for('static', filename='css/modules/social/social_main.css') }}">
</head>

<body class="page-wrapper"><!-- flex 縱向 -->

<!-- ===== 頁首 ===== -->
<header class="custom-header">
  <a href="/" class="back-btn" title="返回首頁">❮</a>

  <form class="search-bar" onsubmit="return false;">
    <input type="text" class="search-input" placeholder="搜尋貼文、使用者…">
    <button type="submit" class="search-btn">🔍</button>
  </form>

  <nav class="social-nav">
    <a href="#"   class="action-btn" title="新增貼文">➕</a>
    <a href="#"              class="action-btn" title="通知">🔔</a>
    <a href="#"              class="action-btn" title="收藏">⭐</a>
    <a href="#"              class="action-btn" title="聊天">💬</a>

    <div class="more-wrapper">
      <button type="button" class="action-btn more-toggle" title="更多">⋯</button>
      <div class="more-menu">
        <button type="button" id="toggle-dark" class="more-item">🌗 深色模式</button>
        <a href="#" class="more-item">⚙️ 個人設定</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </nav>
</header>

<!-- ===== 主要區域：左右雙欄 ===== -->
<div class="content-flex">

  <!-- — 左側固定標籤（獨立滾動） — -->
  <aside class="tag-panel">
    <ul>
      <li data-filter="all"        class="tag active">📋 全部</li>
      <li data-filter="happy"      class="tag">😄 開心</li>
      <li data-filter="sad"        class="tag">😢 難過</li>
      <li data-filter="angry"      class="tag">😡 生氣</li>
      <li data-filter="surprised"  class="tag">😱 驚訝</li>
      <li data-filter="relaxed"    class="tag">😌 放鬆</li>
    </ul>
  </aside>

  <!-- — 右側內容滾動區 — -->
  <section class="scroll-area">

      <!-- --- 公告板 --- -->
    <div class="announcement-board">
      <h2>📌 公告區</h2>

      <!-- 內容跑馬燈放在 body 內，不影響 h2 -->
      <div class="announcement-body">
        <ul class="announcement-scroller">
          <li>🚧 5 / 30 凌晨 00:00 ~ 02:00 系統維護，請使用者提前完成操作。</li>
          <li>🎉 社群聊天室現已推出，歡迎體驗並提供寶貴意見！</li>
          <li>⚠️ 請勿於貼文中透露個人資料，保障帳號安全。</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>


    <!-- --- 貼文清單（示範三篇）--- -->
    <div class="post-list">

      <article class="post-card" data-post-id="101" data-mood="happy">
        <header><strong>小明</strong><span>2025-05-25 09 : 00</span></header>
        <p>今天陽光普照，終於完成馬拉松！🏃‍♂️😄</p>
        <footer>
          <button class="like-btn">👍 12</button>
          <button class="comment-btn">💬 3</button>
          <button class="share-btn">🔗 分享</button>
          <button class="repost-btn">🔁 轉發</button>
          <button class="report-btn">🚩 檢舉</button>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="post-card" data-post-id="102" data-mood="sad">
        <header><strong>匿名</strong><span>2025-05-24 22 : 15</span></header>
        <p>考試失利，有點沮喪…但會振作的！😢</p>
        <footer>
          <button class="like-btn">👍 5</button>
          <button class="comment-btn">💬 0</button>
          <button class="share-btn">🔗 分享</button>
          <button class="repost-btn">🔁 轉發</button>
          <button class="report-btn">🚩 檢舉</button>
        </footer>
      </article>

      <article class="post-card" data-post-id="103" data-mood="surprised">
        <header><strong>小悠</strong><span>2025-05-24 18 : 30</span></header>
        <p>第一次抽獎就中了 Switch！太幸運了😱</p>
        <footer>
          <button class="like-btn">👍 30</button>
          <button class="comment-btn">💬 8</button>
          <button class="share-btn">🔗 分享</button>
          <button class="repost-btn">🔁 轉發</button>
          <button class="report-btn">🚩 檢舉</button>
        </footer>
      </article>

    </div><!-- /post-list -->

  </section><!-- /scroll-area -->

</div><!-- /content-flex -->

<!-- 功能尚未開通彈窗 -->
<div id="feature-modal" class="feature-modal-overlay">
  <div class="feature-modal-box">
    <h3>功能尚未開通</h3>
    <p>很抱歉，這個功能尚未開通，敬請期待！</p>
    <button onclick="closeFeatureModal()">知道了</button>
  </div>
</div>
{% include 'components/footer.html' %}

<script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/base.js') }}"></script>
<script src="{{ url_for('static', filename='js/modules/social/social_main.js') }}"></script>
</body>
</html>

